title: NFL ATL: Geno vs. Vick
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Geno vs. Vick
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the latest NFL news, including the Houston Texans naming a starting quarterback in Ryan Fitzpatrick, the Washington Redskins’ defensive issues and the circus that is the New York Jets’ quarterback competition. Plus, is Kurt Warner a first-ballot Hall of Famer? And which teams can compete with the Seahawks and 49ers in the NFC?
